Why Invest



At Rambus, our innovations make data faster and safer.  Built upon a strong foundation of Leading-edge IP, our technologies and products serve high-growth data center and mobile edge/IoT markets.







Focused on high-growth data center and mobile edge markets
Continued profitable growth through execution and acquisitions
Strong foundation of committed, long-term revenue
High, predictable margin from reoccurring royalties and fees
Strong balance sheet to support strategic initiatives












Quick Facts

NASDAQ: RMBS
Incorporated in 1990
IPO: 1997
Headquartered in Sunnyvale, CA
Operations in North America, Europe and Asia
Q2 ’17 Revenue: $94.7M, up 24% YoY
800+ employees
Over 2,500 patents & applications













